Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.94,0:08:20.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走廊 在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:28.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃果然很厉害 分析得非常准确
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:40.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来又变了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:42.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在到处逃啊 1st
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:54.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟由乃一起果然没错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:56.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妥妥的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.75,0:09:01.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那爆炸 勉强躲过了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:05.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪 接着呢
