Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.71,0:09:13.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.56,0:09:14.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:17.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:22.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪 不光是爆炸 你也要看一下自己会怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:24.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:31.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:34.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是旁观者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:39.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…只把周围的事写进日记
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:45.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个未来日记里面 完全没有写我自己的事
