Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:06.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日记没有变化 进展顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:07.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过总感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:11.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.36,0:13:12.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.95,0:13:14.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高坂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:18.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们应该被威胁不准走出教室的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:20.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在外面走动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:21.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:29.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行不需要检查时间轴 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:32.91,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,200)}阿雪捉住了。\N老师和大家都是敌人！！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行不需要检查时间轴 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:32.91,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,305)}阿雪被带到9th面前了。\N我要去救他。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:32.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美弥音的目的是天野雪辉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:38.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始 停止炸弹的感应器一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.22,0:13:40.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要是能在这段时间内把他交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:44.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就保证不会出现更多的牺牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:47.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先捉住他 抢走手机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:50.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他旁边的女人也要捉住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:54.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把天野雪辉 带到我面前来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.51,0:13:59.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:06.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是伙伴吗 为什么要这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.43,0:14:11.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好别动 美弥音的周围是雷区
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.36,0:14:14.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我啊 阿雪他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:16.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教学楼里面的炸弹也开了传感器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.19,0:14:20.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教室里面的人跑到外面也会爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:24.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是阿雪的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:28.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明说了大家是伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:31.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明对阿雪说大家是伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:33.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪明明这么相信你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.26,0:14:36.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:39.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想杀死阿雪的人才不是伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:43.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我骗了阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:47.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见了 天野雪辉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:49.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保护阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:53.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论牺牲什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:00.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:00.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.27,0:15:03.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:09.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想杀死阿雪的人 全都给我去死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:12.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:15.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来须课长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:16.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:21.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 大家都会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:22.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:24.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:26.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:28.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:30.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 1st
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:32.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会一个人上路的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:36.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10分钟后所有炸弹都会爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:41.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10分钟后？DEAD END的时间是14点04分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:43.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:47.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连渣都不剩 大家一起大团圆…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:51.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别自己一个人兴奋起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:54.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然敢在我的地盘撒野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:58.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于见到你了 1st
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:00.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:04.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说了吗 「我会保护你的」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:09.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来得真晚啊 4th
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:13.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大个人还欺负小孩子啊 9th
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:15.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4th？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:17.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪你会混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:21.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说白了 9th的目的不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:23.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:26.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的日记是「搜查日记」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行不需要检查时间轴 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:30.09,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(370,160)}{\fr11}105/02  09:15\N展开关于连续杀人魔事件\N疑犯的定期会议。\N疑犯可能是火山高夫。\N让搜查员2名跟踪他。\N5/02  13:21\N从公安处收到恐怖分子\N雨流美弥音潜伏在樱见市中的情报。\N5/02  15:31\N西岛以下搜查员2名在学校周边侦查。\N5/02  16:30\N会议。收到火山高夫没有\N不在场证明的消息。\N指示搜查员继续跟踪。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.12,0:16:29.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可以预知一切事件的未来日记
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.27,0:16:33.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我对「神之座」没有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:37.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也不打算让人在我的眼皮底下杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:43.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道你们在聊什么 但我可以说出我的要求吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:49.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那沉默代表「请说」了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:52.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:55.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死1st 然后自杀吧 4th
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.36,0:16:59.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美弥音要胜出游戏 成为神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:03.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此 可以预知未来的警察太碍事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.09,0:17:03.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会听你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:04.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.43,0:17:06.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都得死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:18.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 1st 情况有变
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:21.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要选的话 只能这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:27.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:32.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我这样的废柴 能活下去才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:37.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避着受伤 以旁观者自居
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.35,0:17:43.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己什么都不做 为了获救而利用由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:47.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是该死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.23,0:17:49.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:56.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让…让…我死得…有意义…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.75,0:17:58.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想…死了…还是个废柴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:01.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:10.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去拿回你的日记 1st
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:14.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是证明你不是废柴的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:18.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要只让女人干活 你去打倒9th
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:23.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发抖是你的勇气 不安用笑容来克服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:30.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:32.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:36.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑进雷区…那家伙傻的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:38.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪 左边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:41.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 躲过地雷了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:43.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪 右边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.59,0:18:44.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:47.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是持有者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:51.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4th 你个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:53.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲到左边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:54.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着还是左边…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:55.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.56,0:18:56.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃的指示…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:18:59.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:02.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我亲自引爆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:02.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:10.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:11.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:12.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑过去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:14.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:22.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:24.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9th
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:27.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 糟了糟了糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:30.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.67,0:19:43.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你输了 9th
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:46.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤成这样已经不能动了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:48.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:50.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:52.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟幕…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.91,0:19:56.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的未来日记是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.03,0:19:58.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「逃亡日记」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:11.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9th和其他的持有者一定会再找你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:15.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要捉拿他们 终止这荒唐的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.54,0:20:20.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此 需要天野和我妻 还有我自己的未来日记
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:24.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3人的共同战线 「未来日记同盟」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:27.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教 天野
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:28.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.35,0:20:32.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃 一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:34.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:37.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行不需要检查时间轴 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.99,0:20:38.64,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,170)\fs22}阿雪和由乃结合了。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
